sentences: Mobarak Hossain Khan (27 February 1938 – 24 November 2019) was a Bangladeshi musicologist, musician, and writer.
He also served Radio Bangladesh and former Radio Pakistan for a long stint of 30 years.
Khan died on 24 November 2019 at the age of 81.
